data.description: TREAT YOURSELF! 3-4 BEDROOM 3.5 BATH (1 BEDROOM AND 1 FULL BATHROOM IN THE BASEMENT) RANCH IN GRAND RIDGE! OPEN FLOOR PLAN, HARDWOOD KITCHEN/DINING/ENTRY. MAIN FLOOR HAS FRESH PAINT. SKYLIGHTS WITH RETRACTABLE BLINDS. ROOF REPLACED IN 2015. HIGH EFFICIENCY FURNACE/AC INSTALLED IN 2018. TANKLESS WATER HEATER INSTALLED IN 2018. PARTIALLY FINISHED BASEMENT HAS HUGE REC ROOM, POOL TABLE AND ACCESSORIES INCLUDED. COVERED PATIO OVERLOOKS BACKYARD. LARGE DECK WITH HOT TUB ENCLOSURE, INCLUDES WORKING HOT TUB. ONLY A FEW STEPS FROM THE MASTER BEDROOM FRENCH DOOR TO THE DECK AND HOT TUB. NEIGHBORHOOD PARK AROUND THE BEND. FREEZER IN THE BASEMENT DOES NOT STAY.
